        </section>
        
        <section id="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <p>Our Portal 2 RTX mod introduces numerous visual and technical improvements to enhance your experience:</p>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💡</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Ray Traced Global Illumination</h3>
                    <p>Experience realistic light bounces and color bleeding that bring the test chambers to life.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🪞</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Accurate Reflections</h3>
                    <p>See perfect reflections in glass, polished surfaces, and the iconic portal liquid.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🌑</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Dynamic Shadows</h3>
                    <p>Realistic shadows that respond to all light sources including portal-transmitted light.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💫</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Enhanced Portal Effects</h3>
                    <p>Redesigned portal effects with proper light transmission between linked portals.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎭</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Improved Materials</h3>
                    <p>PBR materials for all surfaces with accurate roughness, metalness, and reflection properties.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚙️</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Performance Optimization</h3>
                    <p>Carefully optimized to run smoothly on a variety of hardware configurations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
