        <section id="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">When will Portal 2 with RTX be released?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We're currently in active development with no fixed release date. Join our Discord for the latest updates on our progress.</p>
                
                <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What are the system requirements?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">For the best experience, we recommend an RTX-capable GPU (NVIDIA RTX 2060 or better). We're also working on optimizations for AMD cards and the Steam Deck.</p>
                
                <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Will this work with the original game or do I need a special version?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our mod will work with the standard Steam version of Portal 2. No special edition required.</p>
                
                <h3 style="color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Will this support co-op play?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Yes! We're ensuring that the co-op campaign will be fully playable with all RTX enhancements.</p>
